{"type":"message","id":"24713117","parentId":"233f5dc9","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:05:42.350Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-17 00:05 EST] Do an overnight-style learning pass on Zara's influences list. For each influence in /Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/LIBRARY.md, produce a short dossier with: (1) 5-sentence summary, (2) 8 'steal this' principles, (3) 3 concrete modern brand/applications, (4) 3 image/visual keywords, (5) 5 primary links (official sites, key essays, interviews, museum pages) with 1-line note each. Organize outputs into /Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/<slug>.md and create a rollup NOTES.md synthesizing cross-cutting patterns + taste gates. Update YES.md where appropriate with tighter 'what to steal' and citations (links). Keep it opinionated and non-generic."}],"timestamp":1771304742348}}
