{"type":"message","id":"83ebd8a4","parentId":"3efa0f58","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:06:05.610Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lcgCn8yv40n0mYEqMvrNXzvk|fc_0b39f6bc9ae76092016993f73a7a2881949be70e1c0fc40c89","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Culture Mag Magazine official website\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 619,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nmagCulture – We love magazines\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://magculture.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe last couple of years has brought a series of indie magazines our way from Africa, so we’re excited to hear this week from Anita Dafeta in Nigeria, who has just published the first issue of Origho Journal, featuring seven creative projects spanning the mediums of film, painting, and photography. Read more ... During February, the magCulture Shop is collaborating with MHL, Margaret Howell’s workwear inspired second line, to present a selection of magazines at MHL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"magculture.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCultured Mag | The Art, Design & Architecture Magazine\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.culturedmag.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCultured Magazine brings you the best from the worlds of contemporary art, design and architecture.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"July 21, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.culturedmag.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOur Culture Mag\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\