{"type":"message","id":"a5af0bdf","parentId":"9f190e7e","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:06:06.567Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1snL4HH2Q1GeYy20iZHTZYMy|fc_0b39f6bc9ae76092016993f73a7a388194a3d7ab954d869d18","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"David Hilliard photographer triptych official website\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 605,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.davidhilliard.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFor years I have been actively documenting my life and the lives of those around me, recording events and attempting to create order in a sometimes chaotic world. While my photographs focus on the personal, the familiar and the simply ordinary, the work strikes a balance between autobiography ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.davidhilliard.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard | Artnet\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.artnet.com/artists/david-hilliard/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard is a contemporary American photographer known for his large-scale color prints. Often arranged as triptychs, from panel to panel, Hilliard shifts the focal plane of the subject, creating a panoramic sense of space. Through his work, the artist probes his identity, tensions, fears, and conflicting emotions about his sexuality while still appealing to a broad audience.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.artnet.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard - The Los Angeles Center of Photography\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://lacphoto.org/people/david-hilliard/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard ( <strong>http://www.davidhilliard.com/</strong>) is a contemporary photographer known for his panoramic photographs. Hilliard was born in Lowell, MA, and received a BFA from the Massachusetts College of Art, before going on to earn an MFA from ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"April 17, 2023\",\n      \"siteName\": \"lacphoto.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard - Artists - Yancey Richardson\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.yanceyrichardson.com/artists/david-hilliard\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHilliard has photographed his father on numerous occasions, and these works exemplify the artist’s ability to fuse fact with fiction. In the triptych Rock Bottom (2008), we see Hilliard’s father standing in a lake on the left panel, and Hilliard himself in the right panel, while the middle panel contains a view across the lake.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.yanceyrichardson.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDavid Hilliard - Biography, Shows, Articles & More | Artsy\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.artsy.net/artist/david-hilliard\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDrawing from his personal life, David Hilliard photographs lush and vivid panoramas. Often staging his scenes, Hilliard presents his works in triptychs—both horizontal and vertical—that capture intimate scenes of human life from slightly varied angles or at different moments.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.artsy.net\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"David Hilliard photographer triptych official website","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":605,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.davidhilliard.com/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFor years I have been actively documenting my life and the lives of those around me, recording events and attempting to create order in a sometimes chaotic world. While my photographs focus on the personal, the familiar and the simply ordinary, the work strikes a balance between autobiography ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.davidhilliard.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard | Artnet\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.artnet.com/artists/david-hilliard/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard is a contemporary American photographer known for his large-scale color prints. Often arranged as triptychs, from panel to panel, Hilliard shifts the focal plane of the subject, creating a panoramic sense of space. Through his work, the artist probes his identity, tensions, fears, and conflicting emotions about his sexuality while still appealing to a broad audience.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.artnet.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard - The Los Angeles Center of Photography\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://lacphoto.org/people/david-hilliard/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard ( <strong>http://www.davidhilliard.com/</strong>) is a contemporary photographer known for his panoramic photographs. Hilliard was born in Lowell, MA, and received a BFA from the Massachusetts College of Art, before going on to earn an MFA from ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"April 17, 2023","siteName":"lacphoto.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard - Artists - Yancey Richardson\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.yanceyrichardson.com/artists/david-hilliard","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHilliard has photographed his father on numerous occasions, and these works exemplify the artist’s ability to fuse fact with fiction. In the triptych Rock Bottom (2008), we see Hilliard’s father standing in a lake on the left panel, and Hilliard himself in the right panel, while the middle panel contains a view across the lake.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.yanceyrichardson.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDavid Hilliard - Biography, Shows, Articles & More | Artsy\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.artsy.net/artist/david-hilliard","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDrawing from his personal life, David Hilliard photographs lush and vivid panoramas. Often staging his scenes, Hilliard presents his works in triptychs—both horizontal and vertical—that capture intimate scenes of human life from slightly varied angles or at different moments.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.artsy.net"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771304766549}}
{"type":"message","id":"da1f86fb","parentId":"a5af0bdf","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:06:07.130Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_koiDted1DhRyh1n0A9FGWjtl|fc_0b39f6bc9ae76092016993f73a7a408194ac2978aa7dda25be","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Anthony Goicolea artist official website\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 564,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.anthonygoicoleastudio.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea · EXHIBITIONS · PAINTING · DRAWING · PHOTOGRAPHY · INSTALLATIONS · SCULPTURE · © Anthony Goicolea | Built with Koken\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.anthonygoicoleastudio.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea | Artnet\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.artnet.com/artists/anthony-goicolea/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea is a contemporary American-Cuban photographer and multi-media artist best known for his self-portraits which explore themes of sexuality, identity, and culture of origin. View Anthony Goicolea’s 229 artworks on artnet. Find an in-depth biography, exhibitions, original artworks for sale, the latest news, and sold auction prices.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.artnet.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea - Biography, Shows, Articles & More | Artsy\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.artsy.net/artist/anthony-goicolea\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nExplore Anthony Goicolea’s biography, achievements, artworks, auction results, and shows on Artsy. Cuban-American artist Anthony Goicolea is known for his elaborately st\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.artsy.net\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea - Wikipedia\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Goicolea\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea (born 1971) is a <strong>New York-based painter, fine art photographer, drafter, and installation artist, born in Atlanta, Georgia</strong>. Goicolea&#x27;s photographs frequently deal with issues of androgyny, homosexuality, and child sexuality. Goicolea was educated at the University of Georgia ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"August 20, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"en.wikipedia.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nArtsuite - Anthony Goicolea - New York, NY - Artist\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://artsuite.com/blogs/community/anthony-goicolea\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAnthony Goicolea is a New York-based multidisciplinary artist whose work ranges from photography, sculpture and video to multi-layered drawings on Mylar and large-scale installations.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"artsuite.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Anthony Goicolea artist official website","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":564,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAnthony Goicolea\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"ht