tographs frequently deal with issues of androgyny, homosexuality, and child sexuality. Goicolea was educated at the University of Georgia ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"August 20, 2025","siteName":"en.wikipedia.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nArtsuite - Anthony Goicolea - New York, NY - Artist\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://artsuite.com/blogs/community/anthony-goicolea","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAnthony Goicolea is a New York-based multidisciplinary artist whose work ranges from photography, sculpture and video to multi-layered drawings on Mylar and large-scale installations.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"artsuite.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771304767114}}
{"type":"message","id":"c09f5ad1","parentId":"da1f86fb","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:06:19.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Creating markdown files**\n\nI need to create markdown files for various influences, like max bense and Carl Jung. I'll craft a consistent template and might use a script to generate the files since there are 35 in total. I think using exec with node or Python could help me create the content. Although writing each file could be cumbersome, I want to keep the dossiers concise, about 250-350 words, with five links each. I’ll use mkdir to organize everything nicely.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0b39f6bc9ae76092016993f74098748194962749d5c6141619\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpk_dKl0rr7Ne026MOSwJ6vDONoqrjhxPhX0rAAHbDIMR5GfO2cdABX59t2tNpJwW9Mid2g74eQWI32VANsajTcYsd8zpeoDCF5oaJ565wjw35VqRUIChbSWTNuue6MWpamcITuvrr6q0YBlgaDsRHmO9fggs45P-RMxMTByQQ65TpX5y4y6Xy6SvLby7k81RI4VOAl4N8dGm_OBaEHfr3mttujUxk4zlLobN17QmtZVG246WJAxWt4IYBk-T2fN5ZgE6cXtclp07ip6gDuh2G13ZBuC9f28b2KXlrAdZLv7wHlTOa_RtHE28oLvvGe2ERVXHt7jXZAUKZOyLMxx2I9UyNo0vykhh7YzqUseBgBCSX8eHxlFuP2vbW3g0lNbDZxU717RzAkr66RdQ_M9oR-jIX7CAzqCMxQFtxJUL1tpXWoZhF1zdb1849Lm4tPmjDBPkhNCuFJl1WJLl5P01RC_PJHgJmkyNrhr72QJro1kRUfgqIDhSViz8twr0zFbNCNakgdSm7VdHn20hAqa0qeNhRnZRysw5Ell0W9NXasMAHM5LDrApWTvmmmlSlFxmubezQg4ZXsSqZvHHcgZ0ckJ3HDHLxp81GBs-kH0_AZ85Ji_raQdtVGTLBVq0StKawbXkocyL3e7znzJ3liBQPeRu-rmbdXWjmsqlBz3Mf-W0IsG6ckDDyQ8-ToZf5ZGIYSpeiM7IbnTKxTAJA_IAoE1rSnoMDWpI45owrAQnZotR2ScSUij_TaTIDpvYiBz8lljqG59BLsMcVBaG_scp2EgJ8UbTzEZ3_TnB-1MBaA1JXwAzhXKd_edUZT9Ko4mU36777WAdRNXBwezqrzek_iy102lU0GUEaE7ol1yZV2drrMoamN82L9uiH5ghJxlY1oDpsbl5eraC5hrVKaDYlRMa7erHVhE_GYxTnNwm1b61PWk-hrOzFcWKPp7ws9TB33oGh6x8Lx2fM3Y-dRkh2DLjdmlbDRwSgxxE2v4Lnb-D5E1oS2Etp6lC3CvVp6XWQ7yb4jA8NrECcsBmkJ0D3CDqzSYvqpays5UtLsi_MV8484W-gp7LFC4uj74Bnm5D8UqQjGTeYvrPou1rYWPOzPsSma821t9vcOeA_n_v6rlu45RdWCAhCFY2zTl7adGKTgOWWRZFrYPZ0k9QQfcUppE6Zn5d1lV94oLdL6DoxMbyKluEwmy8eIzUnwtnJ3mgWYGN