 I need to compile dossiers for Matisse, Picasso, and Klee, and it seems like that's all finished. Now, maybe I should update the library status? But then again, it looks like that's not necessary. So, I'm going to return to the main agent with a summary of what I've done.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Completed the overnight learning pass.\n\n## What I produced\n- Created **dossiers for every influence in** `references/influences/LIBRARY.md` with the requested structure:\n  - 5-sentence summary\n  - 8 “steal this” principles\n  - 3 concrete modern applications\n  - 3 visual keywords\n  - 5 primary links + 1-line note each  \n- Output location (one file per influence):  \n  `references/influences/dossiers/<slug>.md`  \n  (Confirmed present slugs include: `max-bense`, `carl-jung`, `susan-sontag`, `theory-of-the-avant-garde`, `tibor-kalman`, `naoto-fukasawa`, `kenya-hara`, `dieter-rams`, `michael-bierut`, `massimo-vignelli`, `scott-stowell`, `peter-saville`, `bauhaus`, `mies-van-der-rohe`, `james-turrell`, `josef-albers`, `henri-matisse`, `pablo-picasso`, `paul-klee`, `marcel-duchamp`, `virgil-abloh`, `ralph-lauren`, `apc`, `auralee`, `yves-saint-laurent`, `edward-tufte`, `kellogg-on-branding`, `032c`, `i-d`, `the-new-york-times`, `purple-magazine`, `paper-magazine`, `culture-mag-magazine`, `office-magazine`, `gregory-crewdson`, `david-hilliard`, `anthony-goicolea`, `annie-leibovitz`.)\n- Wrote a rollup synthesis:  \n  `references/influences/NOTES.md`  \n  Includes cross-cutting patterns + **taste gates** (Idea Sentence, System Proof, Entropy Budget, Institutional Reality, Ethics of Image, Material Truth) and suggested pairings (e.g., Bense+Sontag, Mies+Turrell, etc.).\n- Updated `references/influences/YES.md` to be **tighter and more operational**, adding **one strong “steal” per influence plus a citation link** (pointing to official/museum/publisher/institutional pages where possible).\n\n## One note for the main agent\n- “**Culture Mag Magazine**” was ambiguous; I treated it as **likely Our Culture Mag** and made that explicit in the dossier + YES entry, with `ourculturemag.com` as the primary reference. If Josh meant a different “Culture Mag,” we should swap the dossier/links later.\n\nFiles are ready for review in the workspace paths above.","textSignature":"msg_0b39f6bc9ae76092016993f9adf7b08194ae59af0b46180940"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.2","usage":{"input":395,"output":629,"cacheRead":42752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43776,"cost":{"input":0.00069125,"output":0.008806,"cacheRead":0.0074816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016978849999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771305385255}}
