{"type":"compaction","id":"3b870b05","parentId":"461b57a2","timestamp":"2026-02-17T05:18:46.173Z","summary":"No prior history.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser requested creation of detailed dossiers for each influence in Zara's library, including summaries, principles, applications, visual keywords, and primary links. Also asked for a rollup NOTES.md and updates to YES.md.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Read LIBRARY.md and YES.md to understand scope\n- Conducted web searches for key figures (Max Bense, Peter Bürger, Scott Stowell, etc.)\n- Created directory structure for dossiers\n- Generated 15 markdown dossiers so far (philosophy/theory and design categories)\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- Currently mid-process creating dossiers (15/35 completed)\n- Following consistent template structure for each\n- Focused on design influences when prefix was cut off\n- Recent work shows dossier creation continuing with art figures (Turrell, Albers, Matisse)\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/LIBRARY.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/YES.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/bauhaus.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/carl-jung.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/dieter-rams.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/henri-matisse.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/james-turrell.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/josef-albers.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/kenya-hara.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/references/influences/dossiers/massimo-vignelli.md\n/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/